1973;;Happy Mother's Day, Love George;;American;;Darren McGavin;;Patricia Neal, Cloris Leachman, Bobby Darin;;thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Happy_Mother%27s_Day,_Love_George;;Teenager Johnny returns to his hometown in New England to try to find out who his father is. There has recently been a string of murders, so Johnny is immediately suspect. In the process of trying to find out who his father is, Johnny discovers that there was an entire story that he did not know.